    Function<org.apache.jena.rdf.model.Resource,FedoraResource>

    public class DefaultIdentifierTranslator
extends PrefixingIdentifierTranslator
    A very simple IdentifierConverter which translates JCR paths into un-dereference-able Fedora subjects (by replacing JCR-specific names with Fedora names). Should not be used except in "embedded" deployments in which no publication of translated identifiers is expected!
    Since:
    May 15, 2013
    Author:
    barmintor, ajs6f, escowles
